{
  "kind": "agent-workflow-platform.workflow",
  "version": 1,
  "exportedAt": "2026-06-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "workflow": {
    "id": "rp-writer-real-vertical-slice-v1",
    "name": "RP Writer Real Vertical Slice V1",
    "version": 1,
    "description": "P-5 vertical slice: playerInput -> worldbook filter -> genericRetriever -> retrievalResultToMarkdown -> markdownMerge(context) -> specializedAgent(rp-writer) -> playerOutput, with inspect branches",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "filterCmd",
        "type": "jsonSource",
        "position": { "x": 100, "y": 50 },
        "config": {
          "data": "{\"operation\": \"filter\", \"selector\": {}}"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "wb",
        "type": "dynamicWorldbook",
        "position": { "x": 350, "y": 50 },
        "config": {
          "resourceRef": "worldbook:rp-tavern",
          "lifecycle": "session",
          "allowedOperations": ["query", "filter"],
          "allowDelete": false
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "input",
        "type": "playerInput",
        "position": { "x": 100, "y": 200 },
        "config": {
          "text": "我把钥匙放到吧台上，看着银铃：\"这件事你打算怎么解释？\""
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "retriever",
        "type": "genericRetriever",
        "position": { "x": 600, "y": 150 },
        "config": {
          "strategy": "keyword",
          "limit": 8
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "retToMd",
        "type": "retrievalResultToMarkdown",
        "position": { "x": 600, "y": 300 },
        "config": {
          "includeScores": false,
          "maxCharsPerEntry": 2000
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "recentMsg",
        "type": "markdownSource",
        "position": { "x": 100, "y": 400 },
        "config": {
          "content": "## Recent Messages\n\n**银铃**: 林舟，仓库的钥匙你保管好。别让老板知道。\n**林舟**: 你就不怕我拿着钥匙跑了？\n**银铃**: 你跑不了。外面下着雨呢。\n**老板**: （从柜台后抬头）你们在聊什么？"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mergeCtx",
        "type": "markdownMerge",
        "position": { "x": 900, "y": 250 },
        "config": {
          "separator": "\n\n---\n\n",
          "skipEmpty": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "preset",
        "type": "markdownSource",
        "position": { "x": 100, "y": 550 },
        "config": {
          "content": "## Style Preset\n\n- Narrative style: 中文文学叙事\n- Perspective: 第三人称有限视角（跟随林舟）\n- Tone: 紧张、悬疑\n- Length: 中等篇幅（200-400字）\n- Format: 纯正文，无章节标题"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent",
        "type": "specializedAgent",
        "position": { "x": 1150, "y": 400 },
        "config": {
          "profileId": "rp-writer",
          "modelId": "mock-model",
          "temperature": 0.8,
          "maxTokens": 2048
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "output",
        "type": "playerOutput",
        "position": { "x": 1400, "y": 400 },
        "config": {
          "displayLabel": "RP Narrative"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "inspWbCorpus",
        "type": "inspectOutput",
        "position": { "x": 900, "y": 50 },
        "config": { "displayMode": "json" }
      },
      {
        "id": "inspRetResult",
        "type": "inspectOutput",
        "position": { "x": 1150, "y": 50 },
        "config": { "displayMode": "json" }
      },
      {
        "id": "inspRetMd",
        "type": "inspectOutput",
        "position": { "x": 1400, "y": 50 },
        "config": { "displayMode": "markdown" }
      },
      {
        "id": "inspContext",
        "type": "inspectOutput",
        "position": { "x": 1400, "y": 200 },
        "config": { "displayMode": "markdown" }
      },
      {
        "id": "inspAgent",
        "type": "inspectOutput",
        "position": { "x": 1400, "y": 550 },
        "config": { "displayMode": "text" }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "id": "e_filter",
        "source": "filterCmd",
        "sourcePort": "json",
        "target": "wb",
        "targetPort": "command"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_corpus",
        "source": "wb",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "retriever",
        "targetPort": "corpus"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_query",
        "source": "input",
        "sourcePort": "text",
        "target": "retriever",
        "targetPort": "query"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_ret_to_md",
        "source": "retriever",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "retToMd",
        "targetPort": "result"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_retmd_left",
        "source": "retToMd",
        "sourcePort": "markdown",
        "target": "mergeCtx",
        "targetPort": "left"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_msg_right",
        "source": "recentMsg",
        "sourcePort": "markdown",
        "target": "mergeCtx",
        "targetPort": "right"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_ctx_to_agent",
        "source": "mergeCtx",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "agent",
        "targetPort": "context"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_user_input",
        "source": "input",
        "sourcePort": "text",
        "target": "agent",
        "targetPort": "userInput"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_preset",
        "source": "preset",
        "sourcePort": "markdown",
        "target": "agent",
        "targetPort": "instruction"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_agent_out",
        "source": "agent",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "output",
        "targetPort": "text"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_insp_wb_corpus",
        "source": "wb",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "inspWbCorpus",
        "targetPort": "jsonInput"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_insp_ret",
        "source": "retriever",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "inspRetResult",
        "targetPort": "jsonInput"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_insp_ret_md",
        "source": "retToMd",
        "sourcePort": "markdown",
        "target": "inspRetMd",
        "targetPort": "markdownInput"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_insp_ctx",
        "source": "mergeCtx",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "inspContext",
        "targetPort": "markdownInput"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_insp_agent",
        "source": "agent",
        "sourcePort": "result",
        "target": "inspAgent",
        "targetPort": "textInput"
      }
    ]
  }
}
